  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: when input field in Chat contains several rows of text (7+ rows), user cut part of this text or all text or just quickly delete symbols,  input field doesn't restore initial state and app becomes unresponsive with this size of input field\r\n![andr_2](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/34380449-2b231de2-eb0a-11e7-9c5b-6da5ec67eb58.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\ninput field restores initial size;\r\napp is responsive.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\ninput field doesn't go back to  initial size;\r\napp is unresponsive.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to Chats\r\n- Open any chat\r\n- Type text which contains more than 7 rows of text \r\n- cut part of it\r\n- quickly delete all remaining text\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: \r\n is reproducible on current develop 27/12 (0.9.11d486)\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nTF session (0:30 - 02:25): https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/7375901/sessions/13/?accessToken=c2gsnGGHnpch6lwZjOwFHwoLMEg",
